WEBVTT

01:31.380 --> 01:34.900
=Generation to Generation=

01:35.020 --> 01:37.940
=Episode 14=

01:38.410 --> 01:39.690
Thank you very much.

01:40.290 --> 01:41.260
Miss Feng.

01:41.540 --> 01:42.380
Mr. Dai.

01:43.900 --> 01:44.850
Miss Feng.

01:48.740 --> 01:50.330
- Village Chief.
- Miss Feng.

01:50.330 --> 01:51.462
Thank you, Miss Feng.

01:51.473 --> 01:52.690
It's a relief you're unharmed.

01:52.690 --> 01:53.540
Village Chief,

01:53.540 --> 01:55.210
weren't you told to hide first?

01:55.210 --> 01:56.109
The Village Chief said

01:56.330 --> 01:58.770
he wouldn't be at ease
until he saw you safe.

01:58.770 --> 02:00.290
Luckily, we made it in time.

02:00.290 --> 02:01.690
Did they make things hard for you?

02:02.290 --> 02:03.210
No, no.

02:03.210 --> 02:04.900
They just locked me up.

02:04.900 --> 02:05.770
I got lucky.

02:05.770 --> 02:06.990
I found a hidden passage

02:07.410 --> 02:09.010
and ran out to meet up with Qingyun.

02:09.340 --> 02:11.410
How fortunate you are.

02:11.980 --> 02:13.500
Many thanks to you both.

02:14.410 --> 02:15.250
Otherwise,

02:15.570 --> 02:18.060
who knows what would've happened?

02:18.220 --> 02:19.570
We've always lived here

02:19.570 --> 02:22.380
by the rules and kept the sect laws.

02:22.380 --> 02:25.610
I truly don't know why they arrested us.

02:25.610 --> 02:27.940
Even if Xing did something wrong,

02:27.940 --> 02:30.340
they shouldn't have taken
the whole village.

02:30.610 --> 02:32.260
Why would they seize the villagers?

02:32.730 --> 02:34.340
We're sect members after all.

02:35.290 --> 02:36.420
One of their own.

02:36.990 --> 02:38.250
They're making corpse slaves.

02:38.730 --> 02:39.910
Corpse slaves?

02:40.500 --> 02:41.500
What are those?

02:42.100 --> 02:43.610
Corpse slaves...

02:45.890 --> 02:46.730
Village Chief,

02:47.100 --> 02:48.100
you've seen them before?

02:49.890 --> 02:51.060
Nineteen years ago,

02:51.660 --> 02:53.690
when the former chief,

02:53.690 --> 02:55.660
Nie Hengcheng, was still alive,

02:55.660 --> 02:56.730
my eldest nephew

02:56.730 --> 02:59.610
was taken and made into a corpse slave.

02:59.610 --> 03:01.500
He died on the Youming Path.

03:02.100 --> 03:03.660
Those turned into corpse slaves

03:03.660 --> 03:05.980
lose all reason
and are controlled by others,

03:05.980 --> 03:09.500
and in the end, their bodies rot away.

03:10.170 --> 03:11.610
After the Battle of Mount Tu,

03:12.170 --> 03:14.940
I thought the nightmare
was finally over.

03:15.260 --> 03:16.100
Yet they've

03:17.060 --> 03:19.090
started again.

03:19.540 --> 03:20.380
Xiaohan,

03:20.690 --> 03:21.540
we must return at once

03:21.540 --> 03:22.380
and report this

03:23.260 --> 03:24.100
to Master.

03:24.290 --> 03:25.730
I fear that before we can report it,

03:25.730 --> 03:27.940
the villagers will be fully refined.

03:28.500 --> 03:31.130
By then, the Hanhai Mountains

03:31.130 --> 03:33.450
and Jianghu will face disaster.

03:34.500 --> 03:35.340
The priority now

03:37.140 --> 03:38.380
is to stop them from continuing

03:38.380 --> 03:40.010
to make corpse slaves.

03:43.100 --> 03:44.380
I know a place

03:44.730 --> 03:45.820
that might

03:45.820 --> 03:47.540
hold a way to stop them.

03:50.100 --> 03:53.740
(Li Sect, Jiuzhou Archive,
Treasured Tomes)

04:02.540 --> 04:03.380
Come.

04:09.260 --> 04:10.780
When I was young,

04:10.780 --> 04:12.170
I once came here to clean.

04:12.500 --> 04:13.380
I heard

04:13.690 --> 04:15.780
this place holds books and records

04:15.780 --> 04:17.780
collected by generations of chiefs.

04:18.700 --> 04:20.730
The former chief disliked reading

04:21.290 --> 04:22.930
and locked this place away.

04:23.610 --> 04:24.610
After his death,

04:25.100 --> 04:26.980
no one remembered it anymore.

04:27.290 --> 04:29.370
I'll look for any texts
that mention corpse slaves.

04:36.700 --> 04:38.500
(Jiuzhou Archive)

04:39.410 --> 04:41.170
Jiuzhou Archive?

04:41.170 --> 04:42.010
Miss Feng,

04:42.540 --> 04:43.780
you've heard of it too?

04:44.610 --> 04:47.850
I once heard a friend mention it.

04:47.850 --> 04:49.020
Was this friend of yours

04:49.020 --> 04:51.580
someone of high standing in the sect?

04:51.580 --> 04:52.660
I only know

04:52.660 --> 04:55.100
he read some books in Jiuzhou Archive

04:55.900 --> 04:58.700
and even found a dragon beast scale.

04:58.980 --> 05:01.850
Your friend must be the Mu kid.

05:10.180 --> 05:12.340
(Yan Xu, Elder Zhibi of Li Sect)

05:13.780 --> 05:14.810
Elder Yan.

05:18.700 --> 05:19.540
Elder Yan,

05:20.020 --> 05:21.370
you're still alive?

05:21.660 --> 05:22.500
Gui,

05:23.810 --> 05:25.290
we haven't met in over ten years,

05:25.290 --> 05:27.203
and the first thing you do
is curse me to death?

05:29.250 --> 05:30.090
Village Chief,

05:31.140 --> 05:32.020
you know him?

05:32.540 --> 05:34.900
This is Elder Zhibi of Li Sect.

05:34.900 --> 05:36.100
Elder Yan,

05:36.100 --> 05:38.410
who specializes
in recording sect history.

05:38.410 --> 05:40.850
I hadn't heard from you for years.

05:40.850 --> 05:43.410
Nie Hengcheng died suddenly

05:43.410 --> 05:44.980
and named no successor.

05:44.980 --> 05:46.410
Nie Zhe took the position improperly,

05:46.410 --> 05:48.140
so he locked me here,

05:48.140 --> 05:50.340
trying to force me
to alter sect history.

05:51.050 --> 05:54.140
A year ago, Mu Qingyan

05:54.140 --> 05:56.660
was gravely injured by Nie Zhe.

05:56.660 --> 05:58.660
Luckily, he hid here.

05:58.660 --> 06:00.580
I saved his life.

06:01.780 --> 06:04.850
With his aloof and unruly nature,

06:04.850 --> 06:07.100
he'd even have friends?

06:08.250 --> 06:09.090
Who are you?

06:09.340 --> 06:10.730
How did you meet him?

06:11.580 --> 06:12.780
After he escaped from here,

06:13.580 --> 06:15.490
he reached Qingzhu Gang to recover.

06:15.980 --> 06:18.050
We learned he was in danger this time,

06:18.700 --> 06:19.900
so we came to help.

06:20.540 --> 06:22.730
No wonder you were going
to Qinglong Altar.

06:22.730 --> 06:23.570
Elder Yan,

06:24.250 --> 06:25.730
you must have examined

06:25.730 --> 06:27.020
all the books here.

06:27.410 --> 06:28.250
Do you know

06:28.610 --> 06:29.700
a cure for corpse slaves?

06:30.980 --> 06:32.340
Corpse slaves?

06:33.580 --> 06:34.930
Didn't they disappear long ago?

06:34.930 --> 06:36.700
Nie Zhe has started refining them again.

06:36.700 --> 06:37.540
I suppose

06:37.930 --> 06:39.810
he means to use them against Mu Qingyan.

06:41.340 --> 06:42.780
That scoundrel Nie Zhe

06:43.490 --> 06:45.140
is becoming
more and more like his uncle.

06:45.140 --> 06:46.980
Ignorant, reckless, and tyrannical.

06:48.730 --> 06:50.730
Let's talk about corpse slaves first.

06:51.660 --> 06:53.020
The records say

06:53.490 --> 06:54.660
corpse slaves are refined

06:54.660 --> 06:57.620
using Gu worms
and Shanci Mushroom poison.

06:57.900 --> 07:01.580
As long as we find herbs
that counter the poison,

07:01.580 --> 07:04.700
we can temporarily suppress
their toxicity.

07:05.490 --> 07:07.710
But I don't know

07:08.140 --> 07:09.850
how to completely remove it.

07:11.810 --> 07:13.580
All things restrain one another.

07:13.580 --> 07:15.930
If we find where Shanci Mushrooms grow,

07:15.930 --> 07:17.490
we'll surely find what counters them.

07:17.930 --> 07:19.140
I know where they grow.

07:19.580 --> 07:20.420
I'll go.

07:20.540 --> 07:21.380
We'll go together.

07:33.340 --> 07:34.490
Why are there so many people?

07:34.633 --> 07:36.006
The EightClaw Prison was destroyed.

07:36.370 --> 07:37.490
To restart the refining pool,

07:37.806 --> 07:39.612
they'll need a large amount
of the mushrooms.

07:40.700 --> 07:42.486
Xiaohan, take care
of the three on the right.

07:43.580 --> 07:44.420
Two.

07:44.730 --> 07:45.570
I'll handle the rest.

07:51.930 --> 07:52.910
The summons has sounded.

07:53.170 --> 07:54.170
Hurry to assemble. Go.

07:54.170 --> 07:55.290
The summons of Li Sect.

07:55.660 --> 07:57.850
Something must've happened
near Xuanwu Altar.

07:58.660 --> 07:59.730
Could it be Mu Qingyan?

08:00.216 --> 08:01.649
Has he begun attacking Xuanwu Altar?

08:02.610 --> 08:03.730
They're using corpse slaves

08:03.730 --> 08:04.580
to deal with him.

08:05.590 --> 08:06.710
Hurry and find the antidote.

08:08.060 --> 08:13.020
(Li Sect, Xuanwu Altar)

08:15.850 --> 08:16.900
Mr. Mu,

08:17.170 --> 08:18.220
over a year ago,

08:18.580 --> 08:19.810
you fled in disgrace.

08:20.100 --> 08:21.850
Everyone thought you were dead.

08:22.250 --> 08:23.490
The Chief was merciful

08:23.980 --> 08:26.370
and even set up a cenotaph for you.

08:26.900 --> 08:28.780
You feel no gratitude for his kindness,

08:29.100 --> 08:30.700
yet you turn on us instead?

08:31.580 --> 08:32.530
Li Sect

08:32.850 --> 08:34.610
belongs to the Mu clan to begin with.

08:34.890 --> 08:36.130
Anyone with sense

08:36.650 --> 08:37.850
wouldn't stop the Young Master.

08:37.850 --> 08:38.850
Shut up, You Guanyue.

08:39.100 --> 08:40.610
Is this your place to speak?

08:40.820 --> 08:42.250
You rose by slick words

08:42.250 --> 08:43.820
and shameless flattery.

08:43.820 --> 08:44.890
Look around.

08:44.890 --> 08:46.370
Who here truly respects you?

08:46.370 --> 08:47.210
You...

08:49.610 --> 08:50.490
Mu Qingyan,

08:50.490 --> 08:52.300
with the strategist here today,

08:52.300 --> 08:53.980
prepare to die.

08:53.980 --> 08:55.180
This time,

08:55.180 --> 08:57.250
you won't even get a cenotaph.

08:57.250 --> 08:58.250
Enough talk.

08:58.250 --> 08:59.110
Young Master,

08:59.130 --> 09:00.130
kill Xiong Qianjin,

09:00.610 --> 09:01.980
and we'll wipe out Xuanwu Altar.

09:02.180 --> 09:03.250
Not me.

09:04.890 --> 09:05.730
You'll do it.

09:08.610 --> 09:09.450
Me?

09:09.730 --> 09:11.130
You'll fight Master Xiong

09:11.130 --> 09:12.130
one-on-one,

09:12.130 --> 09:13.730
fair and square.

09:13.730 --> 09:15.060
If you survive,

09:15.060 --> 09:17.100
then the Xuanwu and Qinglong Altars

09:17.100 --> 09:19.650
will both be under your command.

09:22.300 --> 09:23.580
Young Master,

09:23.580 --> 09:25.730
my skills are lacking.

09:25.730 --> 09:27.130
If I lose by mistake,

09:27.130 --> 09:28.220
my shame is one thing,

09:28.220 --> 09:29.100
but if it dampens

09:29.100 --> 09:30.820
your momentum in reclaiming the sect,

09:31.370 --> 09:32.250
wouldn't that be

09:32.610 --> 09:33.850
an unforgivable sin?

09:34.250 --> 09:36.130
You Guanyue,

09:37.530 --> 09:39.490
you've spent
half your life currying favor,

09:39.820 --> 09:41.980
smiling, and ingratiating yourself.

09:42.530 --> 09:43.940
But that alone isn't enough

09:44.420 --> 09:45.300
to win hearts.

09:46.180 --> 09:47.730
If you want to be an elder

09:47.730 --> 09:48.643
or an enforcer someday,

09:49.610 --> 09:52.420
you'll need to show real skill.

09:53.610 --> 09:54.450
Go.

09:55.100 --> 09:55.940
Kill him.

09:57.340 --> 09:58.820
Consider it your grand opening.

10:04.220 --> 10:05.060
You want me

10:05.700 --> 10:06.980
to fight this piece of trash?

10:06.980 --> 10:08.490
If you can defeat You Guanyue,

10:09.220 --> 10:10.370
I'll spare you today.

10:11.530 --> 10:12.700
You're far too arrogant.

10:12.980 --> 10:13.940
Prepare to die!

10:56.130 --> 10:56.970
You Guanyue,

10:57.490 --> 10:59.180
you'd followed Elder Qiu for years.

10:59.700 --> 11:01.770
He was called the Undying Phoenix,

11:02.770 --> 11:04.940
one who dared to shed his own flesh.

11:55.940 --> 11:57.650
- He won!
- Master You, impressive!

11:57.650 --> 11:58.850
Well done, Master You!

12:13.770 --> 12:15.650
Xiong Qianjin aided evil for years,

12:16.490 --> 12:18.130
slaughtering innocent sect members.

12:18.130 --> 12:20.940
His crimes are countless
and unforgivable.

12:20.940 --> 12:22.420
Killing him today

12:22.420 --> 12:23.730
serves as a warning to all.

12:28.730 --> 12:31.730
As for what comes next,
please enlighten me.

12:31.730 --> 12:35.250
I'll always serve you, Young Master.

12:36.370 --> 12:39.340
We'll always serve you, Young Master.

12:39.340 --> 12:41.060
Flatten Xuanwu Altar.

12:42.300 --> 12:43.140
Kill them!

12:44.580 --> 12:46.730
Charge!

12:58.730 --> 12:59.730
Time is tight.

12:59.730 --> 13:00.580
How do these herbs

13:00.980 --> 13:02.820
counter the Shanci Mushroom poison?

13:02.831 --> 13:04.311
You go back
to Jiuzhou Archive first.

13:04.322 --> 13:06.234
I'll catch a corpse slave
to test the medicine.

13:06.245 --> 13:07.125
- Sure.
- No need.

13:07.770 --> 13:08.610
I'll do it.

13:19.700 --> 13:20.940
When were you poisoned?

13:23.100 --> 13:24.340
No time for this.

13:24.340 --> 13:25.940
Test the medicine first. If it fails,

13:25.940 --> 13:27.530
kill me with one strike.

13:27.530 --> 13:29.100
Then find a place and bury me.

13:29.100 --> 13:30.426
Just take the Sunshine Blade back.

13:30.980 --> 13:31.980
Don't talk nonsense.

13:32.370 --> 13:33.250
It won't come to that.

13:55.730 --> 13:56.890
Why are you so distracted?

13:57.370 --> 13:59.060
I was just thinking about Zhao.

13:59.490 --> 14:01.370
She's been ill for nearly a month now.

14:01.770 --> 14:03.010
I wonder when she'll recover.

14:03.340 --> 14:05.060
She left to find Chang Ning, right?

14:06.060 --> 14:07.340
How do you know?

14:07.700 --> 14:09.850
She took the herbal incense
I prepared for Chang Ning.

14:10.530 --> 14:11.490
That child,

14:11.770 --> 14:13.220
bold and decisive by nature,

14:14.010 --> 14:15.130
is very much like her aunt.

14:15.610 --> 14:16.700
Chang must've gone

14:17.340 --> 14:19.010
to seek revenge against the demon sect.

14:20.730 --> 14:21.700
Uncle Lei,

14:21.700 --> 14:22.770
tell me.

14:22.770 --> 14:25.060
What is this demon sect like?

14:25.060 --> 14:25.900
Is it dangerous?

14:26.420 --> 14:27.370
Is it dangerous?

14:31.580 --> 14:32.730
We'll see

14:34.793 --> 14:35.780
if she comes back intact.

15:03.420 --> 15:04.260
Yu Huiyin.

15:20.250 --> 15:21.340
Corpse slaves.

15:21.340 --> 15:23.220
Nie Zhe is using
corpse slaves against us.

15:23.220 --> 15:25.340
Young Master,
these corpse slaves feel no pain.

15:25.340 --> 15:26.753
They can't be killed; what do we do?

15:31.490 --> 15:32.330
Break!

15:34.980 --> 15:35.820
Mr. Mu,

15:36.770 --> 15:39.285
you led men to attack my Xuanwu Altar.

15:39.296 --> 15:41.010
Aren't you afraid
the Chief will punish you

15:41.010 --> 15:42.980
and order your execution,

15:42.980 --> 15:44.340
disregarding your families' ties?

15:44.340 --> 15:46.180
Master Shangguan, don't joke.

15:46.180 --> 15:47.980
Nie Zhe is using sect members' lives

15:47.980 --> 15:49.580
to refine corpse slaves.

15:49.580 --> 15:51.530
He's broken a century-old sect rule.

15:52.770 --> 15:54.490
What family ties are left to speak of?

15:55.010 --> 15:57.530
The Chief hasn't touched
a single core member.

15:57.850 --> 15:59.770
He's only used

15:59.770 --> 16:01.340
low-cultivation commoners.

16:01.340 --> 16:02.530
The Chief said

16:02.530 --> 16:03.580
these people

16:03.580 --> 16:04.850
are nothing but vermin.

16:04.850 --> 16:06.180
Even commoners

16:06.180 --> 16:08.255
are loved ones of sect disciples.

16:08.266 --> 16:09.770
How can Nie Zhe trample them at will?

16:09.770 --> 16:10.610
Enough provocation.

16:11.580 --> 16:13.730
You're about to die
and still spout nonsense.

16:27.730 --> 16:28.940
Strike the neck and spine.

17:11.810 --> 17:12.670
Mr. Yu,

17:12.700 --> 17:13.540
I'll assist you.

17:21.620 --> 17:22.460
Are you okay?

17:30.140 --> 17:32.180
I saw something was wrong
with you long ago.

17:32.570 --> 17:33.420
Shangguan Haonan,

17:33.860 --> 17:36.090
you truly are a traitor.

17:36.380 --> 17:37.220
Yu Huiyin,

17:37.940 --> 17:39.180
you aid evil

17:39.810 --> 17:41.490
and slaughter sect members with Nie Zhe.

17:42.050 --> 17:43.816
Once the truth
of the corpse slaves spreads,

17:44.523 --> 17:46.490
let's see who in the sect
will still support you.

17:46.940 --> 17:47.780
Dead men

17:48.220 --> 17:49.380
don't speak.

18:42.490 --> 18:43.860
So, the poison in you

18:44.730 --> 18:46.090
was never fully cured.

18:47.900 --> 18:48.740
Young Master!

18:52.860 --> 18:53.700
Young Master,

18:54.176 --> 18:55.356
I'll carve a path out for you.

18:56.530 --> 18:58.010
Fate has favored me.

19:09.770 --> 19:10.610
Xing...

19:24.380 --> 19:26.180
Young Master, don't hurt her.

20:59.050 --> 20:59.980
Demoness,

20:59.980 --> 21:01.140
you're Cai Pingshu's...

21:21.140 --> 21:21.980
Mu Qingyan!

21:30.660 --> 21:31.620
Are you okay?

22:14.090 --> 22:14.980
You're awake.

22:16.530 --> 22:17.370
Zhao,

22:20.290 --> 22:21.330
you're here.

22:34.415 --> 22:36.462
The herbal incense has been burning
for four hours.

22:37.180 --> 22:38.490
How do you feel?

22:43.180 --> 22:44.020
I'm fine.

22:50.420 --> 22:53.180
Uncle Lei prepared
this herbal incense for you.

22:53.180 --> 22:54.900
It contains dozens of herbs.

22:54.900 --> 22:57.290
It can't eradicate your poison,

22:58.220 --> 22:59.700
but it can suppress it for now.

23:01.940 --> 23:03.090
So, you already know.

23:17.090 --> 23:17.940
You know,

23:18.570 --> 23:19.770
the Li Sect's tailoring craft

23:19.770 --> 23:21.069
is no worse than Granny Needle's.

23:23.090 --> 23:24.380
You look handsome in this outfit.

23:24.903 --> 23:26.056
Like someone from a painting.

23:29.010 --> 23:30.330
So, you're here

23:31.090 --> 23:33.050
to pity a dying man like me?

23:35.700 --> 23:36.770
Everyone dies.

23:37.290 --> 23:39.620
Some die sooner;

23:39.860 --> 23:40.770
some die later.

23:41.180 --> 23:42.570
There is nothing strange about it.

23:42.940 --> 23:44.220
Why would I pity you?

23:45.140 --> 23:46.420
Ever since I can remember,

23:46.940 --> 23:48.730
I knew my aunt was nearing the end.

23:50.490 --> 23:51.660
But I never felt

23:52.570 --> 23:53.860
she needed anyone's pity.

23:54.660 --> 23:56.220
The day before she passed,

23:56.220 --> 23:57.860
she even made Smiley with me.

23:58.980 --> 24:01.290
It was fragrant and sweet that day.

24:02.220 --> 24:03.060
She said

24:04.050 --> 24:05.576
her wishes in this life were fulfilled.

24:05.810 --> 24:06.860
Even if she died,

24:07.290 --> 24:08.329
she would have no regrets.

24:10.980 --> 24:12.220
So, are you here

24:13.380 --> 24:14.620
to help me fulfill my wish?

24:15.090 --> 24:17.090
I'll use every possible way to save you.

24:17.090 --> 24:18.380
If I cannot save you,

24:18.380 --> 24:19.380
I will help you

24:19.380 --> 24:20.490
fulfill your wish.

24:20.810 --> 24:22.140
If you want revenge,

24:22.820 --> 24:23.980
I will help you take revenge.

24:24.620 --> 24:25.660
What then?

24:26.180 --> 24:27.020
Then?

24:29.380 --> 24:31.570
I'll go back to Qingque sect with Yuzhi?

24:45.530 --> 24:46.370
Don't leave.

24:47.860 --> 24:49.330
Okay, I won't.

24:51.250 --> 24:52.420
All right.

24:52.900 --> 24:54.446
I'll leave after I finish things, okay?

25:00.940 --> 25:02.250
Zhao, this is...

25:02.250 --> 25:03.380
People slip up sometimes.

25:03.380 --> 25:04.420
Horses stumble too.

25:04.420 --> 25:05.980
It just happened by accident.

25:05.980 --> 25:07.180
Don't worry.

25:07.180 --> 25:09.010
I've found herbs to suppress the poison.

25:09.380 --> 25:11.140
If the Gu worms aren't cleared in time,

25:12.380 --> 25:13.530
they'll erode your mind.

25:14.253 --> 25:16.279
You'll lose your senses and die.
Do you know that?

25:25.380 --> 25:26.240
I'm sorry.

25:26.250 --> 25:27.600
We've only been apart for days,

25:28.560 --> 25:30.296
and you've turned yourself
into this state.

25:31.770 --> 25:32.610
It's fine.

25:32.770 --> 25:33.703
The fortune teller said

25:33.900 --> 25:35.010
I'd live a long life.

25:35.636 --> 25:36.570
I don't believe in fate.

25:37.570 --> 25:38.730
I only believe in myself.

25:40.380 --> 25:41.490
What are you trying to do?

25:43.157 --> 25:45.223
Thankfully, we have the medicine
Miss Feng brought.

25:45.940 --> 25:47.490
Xing should wake up soon.

25:48.250 --> 25:49.090
Be gentle.

25:51.220 --> 25:52.620
I'm performing acupuncture on Xing.

25:53.140 --> 25:55.090
Why do you hurt more than she does?

25:58.050 --> 25:59.530
Xing, forgive me.

26:04.940 --> 26:05.966
You're so clumsy.

26:05.977 --> 26:06.917
You're driving me crazy.

26:08.279 --> 26:09.409
Why don't you do it yourself?

26:10.050 --> 26:11.220
If I weren't injured,

26:11.620 --> 26:12.620
would I need you?

26:13.940 --> 26:15.860
A fence-sitter
who only knows how to talk.

26:15.860 --> 26:16.700
I...

26:18.180 --> 26:19.620
At least I'm not like you,

26:19.620 --> 26:21.176
living off flattery toward Nie Zhe,

26:21.187 --> 26:22.832
holding a post without doing any work.

26:22.843 --> 26:23.860
Who are you talking about?

26:23.860 --> 26:25.193
Whoever gets angry is who I mean.

26:25.480 --> 26:26.420
Are you feeling guilty?

26:26.420 --> 26:27.330
You Guanyue.

26:32.450 --> 26:33.300
Xing.

26:33.330 --> 26:34.170
Xing.

26:36.010 --> 26:38.010
So naggy that my ears hurt.

26:38.730 --> 26:39.570
Go away.

26:40.620 --> 26:41.770
Do you feel unwell?

26:43.940 --> 26:44.980
Take me to Miss Feng.

26:49.620 --> 26:50.460
Xing.

26:53.980 --> 26:55.420
- Xing.
- Xing.

26:55.420 --> 26:56.260
Xing.

27:00.380 --> 27:01.220
Mr. Dai.

27:03.250 --> 27:05.900
Thanks to you and Miss Feng
for saving my life.

27:05.900 --> 27:08.330
It seems the Gu poison in you has eased.

27:09.220 --> 27:10.490
My Xing is fine.

27:10.810 --> 27:12.730
No need for you to worry.

27:13.010 --> 27:13.850
That's good then.

27:14.170 --> 27:15.243
I came to look for Xiaohan.

27:15.620 --> 27:16.620
What a coincidence.

27:16.620 --> 27:17.856
We're also here for Miss Feng.

27:17.867 --> 27:19.900
She and the Young Master
spent the night together.

27:19.900 --> 27:21.090
They must be

27:21.090 --> 27:22.730
deeply in love

27:22.730 --> 27:24.220
and inseparable now.

27:24.220 --> 27:25.060
Get lost.

27:26.250 --> 27:27.090
Zhao...

27:28.860 --> 27:31.140
Your valor conquered Xuanwu Altar.

27:31.140 --> 27:33.330
Xing and I came to offer
congratulations and thanks.

27:36.180 --> 27:38.090
Did you argue with Xiaohan?

27:39.730 --> 27:41.980
I wanted to take Zhao's pulse
and examine her,

27:41.980 --> 27:43.180
but she refused.

27:43.570 --> 27:44.410
Examine her...

27:45.810 --> 27:46.650
Examine her?

27:47.140 --> 27:47.980
Mr. Mu,

27:48.660 --> 27:49.980
is there a way to fully eradicate

27:49.980 --> 27:50.993
the Gu poison in Xiaohan?

27:51.730 --> 27:52.810
Yan Xu fears Nie Zhe,

27:53.286 --> 27:54.766
so he must be holding something back.

27:55.250 --> 27:57.380
I'll go to Jiuzhou Archive now

27:57.670 --> 27:58.610
to find Yan Xu.

28:02.250 --> 28:03.140
We just settled here.

28:03.140 --> 28:04.369
There's much work awaiting you.

28:04.610 --> 28:05.349
Besides,

28:05.360 --> 28:07.446
you've fought several rounds
with unhealed injuries.

28:08.010 --> 28:08.850
I'm fine.

28:09.810 --> 28:10.650
Mr. Mu,

28:10.733 --> 28:11.740
let me go find Elder Yan.

28:12.220 --> 28:13.180
You stay here.

28:13.180 --> 28:14.330
If Nie Zhe counterattacks,

28:14.330 --> 28:15.170
you'll be ready.

28:23.620 --> 28:24.460
Senior,

28:24.660 --> 28:25.810
do you feel any better today?

28:27.570 --> 28:29.090
Same as always.

28:29.620 --> 28:31.330
Just barely hanging on.

28:32.420 --> 28:33.260
Senior,

28:34.180 --> 28:35.810
Mu Qingyan is advancing aggressively.

28:36.900 --> 28:38.010
In a few days,

28:38.530 --> 28:40.250
he'll likely attack Bliss Palace.

28:40.250 --> 28:41.730
You useless thing.

28:41.730 --> 28:44.980
You've ruled the sect for over ten years
on your uncle's behalf,

28:44.980 --> 28:48.700
yet now you're being beaten
by that Mu brat.

28:48.700 --> 28:50.900
If not for Shangguan's betrayal

28:51.810 --> 28:53.730
and Yu Huiyin and Fengge's injuries,

28:54.596 --> 28:56.200
how would I have fallen into this state?

28:56.700 --> 28:57.540
Senior,

28:58.490 --> 28:59.860
please give me some guidance.

29:01.940 --> 29:04.010
You wouldn't just watch Uncle's legacy

29:04.010 --> 29:04.970
be destroyed, would you?

29:09.700 --> 29:13.090
If my legs hadn't been crippled
by Cai Pingshu,

29:13.090 --> 29:14.530
how would it come to this?

29:15.220 --> 29:16.060
Very well.

29:16.700 --> 29:19.140
Lure that Mu brat here.

29:19.140 --> 29:22.180
I'll eliminate this threat to the sect.

29:24.330 --> 29:25.170
Shangguan,

29:25.490 --> 29:26.900
you traitorous wretch.

29:27.290 --> 29:28.730
The Chief trusted you so deeply,

29:29.180 --> 29:30.330
yet you betrayed him.

29:30.860 --> 29:32.210
How fickle

29:32.490 --> 29:33.660
and ungrateful.

29:34.220 --> 29:35.330
The Young Master arrives.

29:43.810 --> 29:44.650
Young Master,

29:44.860 --> 29:46.380
all forces of Xuanwu Altar are here,

29:46.700 --> 29:47.660
awaiting your judgment.

29:50.940 --> 29:52.490
Crooked mouth and slanted eyes.

29:52.490 --> 29:53.330
Kill him.

29:54.490 --> 29:55.490
- Go.
- Let me go.

29:55.490 --> 29:56.490
Let me go.

29:59.900 --> 30:01.090
Shifty-eyed and sneaky.

30:01.730 --> 30:02.570
Kill him.

30:02.860 --> 30:03.700
What are you doing?

30:04.050 --> 30:06.010
- Let me go.
- Two-faced turncoat.

30:06.380 --> 30:07.220
Kill him.

30:07.231 --> 30:07.971
What are you doing?

30:07.982 --> 30:09.010
- Go.
- No more nonsense.

30:09.010 --> 30:10.250
He can't tell grain from millet.

30:10.250 --> 30:11.180
Kill him.

30:11.180 --> 30:12.900
Lazy and useless.

30:12.900 --> 30:13.740
Kill him.

30:13.820 --> 30:14.690
Young Master.

30:14.810 --> 30:15.770
Spare my life.

30:15.770 --> 30:16.900
Talkative

30:16.900 --> 30:18.250
and meddlesome.

30:18.900 --> 30:19.740
Kill them all.

30:21.940 --> 30:23.140
- Spare me.
- Spare me.

30:23.860 --> 30:25.180
We're willing to surrender.

30:25.180 --> 30:26.700
Young Master, spare us.

30:26.700 --> 30:28.220
Please, spare us.

30:28.220 --> 30:30.290
Get up.

30:31.140 --> 30:32.570
Go.

30:32.570 --> 30:34.140
Are you really going to kill them all?

30:37.700 --> 30:38.980
They're nothing but people

30:38.980 --> 30:40.420
who repeatedly broke sect rules

30:40.420 --> 30:41.810
and are drenched in blood.

30:42.980 --> 30:43.820
Why not?

30:44.220 --> 30:46.380
But such a large Xuanwu Altar

30:46.380 --> 30:47.330
still needs people

30:47.330 --> 30:48.660
to handle odds and ends.

30:49.180 --> 30:50.490
It might be better to keep a few.

30:51.140 --> 30:52.570
They're all top-tier fighters.

30:53.140 --> 30:55.700
They'd cause grudges between us
and those they once persecuted,

30:56.530 --> 30:58.220
or even waver and secretly collude

30:58.770 --> 31:01.250
with Nie Zhe.

31:02.570 --> 31:03.770
Before yesterday's battle,

31:04.330 --> 31:05.770
the Young Master ordered me

31:05.770 --> 31:07.620
to leave a corner open in the northeast

31:08.140 --> 31:10.330
so the weak-willed could escape.

31:10.330 --> 31:11.700
Those who stayed to resist

31:12.620 --> 31:13.940
are all utterly loyal

31:13.940 --> 31:15.093
to Nie Zhe and Xiong Qianjin.

31:15.490 --> 31:16.330
What use are they?

31:17.730 --> 31:19.420
So, you've filtered them out.

31:19.980 --> 31:22.140
I was short-sighted.

31:22.140 --> 31:23.770
You and Shangguan are both soft-hearted.

31:24.730 --> 31:25.730
Handing them to you

31:26.220 --> 31:27.290
would inevitably be a risk.

31:28.090 --> 31:30.490
All these years, you dealt cautiously

31:30.839 --> 31:31.966
with Nie Zhe and his faction.

31:33.490 --> 31:34.660
Thanks for your efforts.

31:36.980 --> 31:37.820
From now on,

31:39.330 --> 31:41.900
I'll return to you
a clean and pure sect.

31:46.380 --> 31:48.010
Ever since you were injured by Nie Zhe

31:48.010 --> 31:48.850
and went missing,

31:49.250 --> 31:50.770
I nearly failed endure.

31:52.180 --> 31:53.770
I always remembered your kindness

31:53.770 --> 31:55.290
and found ways
to maneuver among them.

31:55.660 --> 31:57.530
But watching them harm sect members

31:57.530 --> 31:58.980
was truly tormenting.

31:58.980 --> 31:59.820
Nie kept

32:00.940 --> 32:02.660
probing and testing me.

32:04.140 --> 32:05.620
Life was unbearable.

32:06.250 --> 32:08.730
Dealing with that suspicious rat?

32:10.220 --> 32:11.060
Shangguan,

32:11.570 --> 32:12.770
it hasn't been easy for you.

32:17.910 --> 32:18.860
You did very well.

32:20.490 --> 32:21.990
I had you investigate something.

32:22.290 --> 32:23.130
What did you find?

32:23.623 --> 32:25.140
When I was young in the Demonic Camp,

32:25.980 --> 32:27.730
I once saw Elder Tianji Duan Jiuxiu

32:27.730 --> 32:29.256
use the Wudu Palm to kill for practice.

32:29.810 --> 32:30.776
But from my observation,

32:31.250 --> 32:32.140
what Nie Zhe practices

32:32.700 --> 32:34.180
has the moves but lacks inner force.

32:34.570 --> 32:36.186
He hasn't truly mastered the Wudu Palm.

32:36.490 --> 32:37.570
(It's not the Wudu Palm?)

32:38.770 --> 32:40.420
(Then what is the poison in my body?)

32:43.620 --> 32:44.460
Young Master,

32:44.860 --> 32:46.770
Mr. Dai has brought Elder Yan Xu.

32:54.730 --> 32:55.570
I don't know.

32:56.290 --> 32:58.530
And even if I did, I wouldn't tell you.

32:58.530 --> 32:59.530
Stop bothering with that.

32:59.530 --> 33:00.490
Hurry and send me back.

33:02.290 --> 33:03.770
If you refuse to speak,

33:04.700 --> 33:05.860
I can only tell Nie Zhe

33:06.570 --> 33:08.030
that when I fled the sect back then,

33:08.570 --> 33:09.940
it was you who helped me.

33:09.940 --> 33:10.940
You...

33:10.940 --> 33:12.900
If you're willing to share something,

33:13.620 --> 33:14.460
I guarantee

33:14.770 --> 33:16.530
that before I take over Bliss Palace,

33:17.010 --> 33:19.090
I never once met you.

33:20.860 --> 33:22.180
Excellent.

33:22.810 --> 33:25.290
When you take Bliss Palace,

33:25.290 --> 33:27.330
I'll personally congratulate you.

33:29.810 --> 33:31.020
I've never seen a fence-sitter

33:31.030 --> 33:32.530
be so fresh and shameless.

33:34.050 --> 33:35.485
You little brat.

33:35.496 --> 33:37.250
(Qinglong Altar)
I've said it several times.

33:37.250 --> 33:38.730
You dragged me here for no reason

33:38.730 --> 33:41.180
just to ask
about this Gu-clearing method.

33:41.180 --> 33:42.730
I truly haven't seen it.

33:43.330 --> 33:44.900
How many times do you want to ask?

33:45.220 --> 33:46.730
Corpse slaves first appeared

33:46.860 --> 33:48.380
19 years ago, in early spring.

33:49.220 --> 33:51.860
You know
the former chief's movements best.

33:52.610 --> 33:54.230
Do you recall whether Nie Hengcheng

33:54.287 --> 33:55.493
visited any special place then?

33:58.000 --> 33:59.490
This matter...

34:00.570 --> 34:01.770
I think I remember.

34:02.050 --> 34:03.380
That March,

34:03.980 --> 34:06.570
the former leader often went
near the Youming Path.

34:06.570 --> 34:08.050
There was a herbal garden inside.

34:08.050 --> 34:10.210
Every time he went there,

34:10.210 --> 34:12.610
he'd stay for quite a while.

34:13.626 --> 34:14.759
Where is this herbal garden?

34:18.980 --> 34:20.650
It's a secret realm of the Nie clan.

34:20.650 --> 34:22.380
Outsiders don't know.

34:27.010 --> 34:28.490
The Youming Path...

34:29.490 --> 34:31.260
Lady Sun, it's so late.

34:31.260 --> 34:33.340
Why are you in such a remote place?

34:33.340 --> 34:34.526
Picking flowers for the Chief.

34:35.090 --> 34:37.650
These flowers must have night dew

34:37.650 --> 34:39.130
to be effective.

34:39.130 --> 34:41.050
(Is the place
where Lady Sun picked flowers)

34:41.050 --> 34:42.380
(the herbal garden?)

34:42.380 --> 34:43.780
I know a place.

34:43.780 --> 34:45.130
The herbal garden might be there.

34:45.550 --> 34:46.420
I'll go with you.

34:46.420 --> 34:47.260
Let's go.

34:48.170 --> 34:49.010
Don't go.

34:49.340 --> 34:50.653
I've prepared a decoction for you

34:50.840 --> 34:52.373
to suppress the Gu poison in your body.

34:52.650 --> 34:53.490
Mr. Dai,

34:54.530 --> 34:55.420
may we talk privately?

35:03.321 --> 35:13.981
=Generation to Generation=

35:32.741 --> 35:37.151
♪The breeze is gentle,
and spring is fair♪

35:37.716 --> 35:42.331
♪I roam the rivers and hills
in the martial world♪

35:42.671 --> 35:47.236
♪With a shining cup,
I drink with delight tonight♪

35:47.761 --> 35:52.061
♪Free to wander in the world♪

35:55.006 --> 35:59.706
♪I drink with the breeze,
lost in my dreams♪

36:00.231 --> 36:04.521
♪I rest beneath the stars' soft gleam♪

36:05.181 --> 36:09.211
♪The night is calm, still as a stream♪

36:09.526 --> 36:14.651
♪It washes away all judgment and scheme♪

36:15.226 --> 36:20.036
♪I drink with the breeze,
lost in my dreams♪

36:20.251 --> 36:24.421
♪I hold the bright moon
as I return home♪

36:25.146 --> 36:29.081
♪I freely roam in the world♪

36:29.581 --> 36:34.856
♪All I ask is that you go with me♪

36:57.586 --> 37:02.716
♪I drink with the breeze,
lost in my dreams♪

37:03.081 --> 37:07.451
♪I hold the bright moon
as I return home♪

37:07.716 --> 37:11.846
♪I freely roam in the world♪

37:12.031 --> 37:17.606
♪All I ask is that you go with me♪
